			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<b>Description</b></p>
<p>
Roadtrippers is looking for software developers to help us build solutions to fragmentation problems in road travel planning. You will be developing key features of our web application.</p>
<p>
<strong>What is Roadtrippers?</strong></p>
<p>
Roadtrippers is a fast growing, venture funded startup based in OTR, Cincinnati. Our engaging map based web and mobile experience helps road travelers discover, plan and book the best places and experiences, curated by local experts and travel writers.</p>
<p>
<strong>You need:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience with full stack web development and versatile across client, server and database</li>
<li>
Passion for building an awesome consumer facing product, used by thousands every day</li>
<li>
Rampant hunger for learning, self improvement and willingness to accept constructive criticism</li>
<li>
A good sense of humor &amp; healthy enjoyment of chilled malt beverages :)<br />
&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>
